examples.trace:
Initialize freq={}
i=0: element=1, not in freq → freq={1:1}
i=1: element=2, not in freq → freq={1:1,2:1}
i=2: element=1, in freq → freq={1:2,2:1}
Return {1:2, 2:1}

Initialize freq={}
i=1: element=5, not in freq → freq={5:1}
i=2: element=5, in freq → freq={5:2}
i=3: element=5, in freq → freq={5:3}
Return {5:3}
